I guess I just woke up in a funk this morning.

25
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:19,540
我要把车修好
I need to get my car fixed.

26
00:02:20,380 --> 00:02:23,370
辛蒂，我是乔尔
Hi, Cindy. It's Joel. Joel!

27
00:02:23,510 --> 00:02:25,420
乔尔啦

28
00:02:25,570 --> 00:02:26,990
我今天不舒服
I don't feel very well today.

29
00:02:28,390 --> 00:02:30,500
应该不是食物中毒
no, food poisoning, I think

30
00:02:31,060 --> 00:02:33,500
这里的海滩冷死人了
It's goddamn freezing on this beach.

31
00:02:34,020 --> 00:02:37,050
二月的蒙托克美极了
Montauk in February - brilliant, Joel.

32
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,080
有几页撕掉了
Pages ripped out. Don't remember doing that.

33
00:02:41,220 --> 00:02:42,610
不记得有这回事

34
