since I'm incapable of making eye contact

40
00:03:21,830 --> 00:03:23,730
with a woman I don't know.

41
00:03:25,030 --> 00:03:27,600
或许我该回头找娜欧蜜
Maybe I should get back together with naomi.

42
00:03:28,300 --> 00:03:29,540
她是个好女孩
She was nice.

43
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:31,590
好就够了
nice is good.

44
00:03:33,790 --> 00:03:35,070
她爱我
She loved me.

45
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:15,580
我怎么会见一个爱一个？
Why do I fall in love with every woman I see...

46
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:19,500
对我没兴趣的我也爱？
who shows me the least bit of interest?

47
00:04:40,590 --> 00:04:45,220
“蒙托克”

48
00:05:00,110 --> 00:05:01,460
你好
Hi.

49
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:02,890
你说什么？
I'm sorry?

50
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,460
我在向你问好
I just said hi.

51
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,810
你好
Hi, hello.

52
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:06,990
你好

53
00:05:07,730 --> 00:05:09,080
可以坐近一点吗？
Okay if I sit closer?

54
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,360
你要去多远？
How far are you going?

55
00:05:14,030 --> 00:05:15,720
