Rockville Center.

56
00:05:15,870 --> 00:05:17,890
不会吧，跟我一样
Me, too.

57
00:05:18,030 --> 00:05:18,900
真的吗？
Really?

58
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:21,260
有多少人能殊途同归？
What are the odds?

59
00:05:23,180 --> 00:05:24,840
你很面熟耶
Do I know you?

60
00:05:28,190 --> 00:05:29,780
有没有在诚品买过书？
Do you ever shop at Barnes and noble?

61
00:05:29,930 --> 00:05:30,960
有啊
Sure.

62
00:05:31,110 --> 00:05:32,220
那就对了
That's it! I've seen you.

63
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:32,950
怎样？

64
00:05:33,090 --> 00:05:34,720
我见过你

65
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:37,400
我在那里当过…
Book slave there for five years now.

66
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:38,830
五年的廉价劳工

67
00:05:38,970 --> 00:05:39,880
天哪
I would have thought I would remember you.

68
00:05:40,020 --> 00:05:42,450
结果我认不出你 五年了吗？

69
00:05:42,590 --> 00:05:43,870
可能是头发吧
It might be the hair.

70
00:05:44,470 --> 00:05:45,480
怎样？
What might?

71
00:05:45,620 --> 00:05:47,240
变得了很多
It changes a lot. The color.

72
00:05:47,740 --> 00:05:49,850
发色吧，难怪你认不出我
That's why you might not recognize me.

73
00:05:50,350 --> 00:05:51,110
这是颓废蓝
It's called Blue Ruin.

74
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:52,790
这样啊
The color.

75
00:05:53,410 --> 00:05:54,480
名字很炫吧？
Snappy name, huh?

76
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:56,740
我喜欢 是啊
I like it.

77
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,740
这家公司生产了
This company makes a whole line of colors with snappy names.

78
00:06:00,890 --> 00:06:02,770
各种名字很炫的颜色

79
00:06:02,910 --> 00:06:06,660
血腥红、狂热黄、革命绿
Red Menace, Yellow Fever, Green Revolution...

80
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:09,370
