That would be a job, coming up with those names.

81
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:12,370
有那种工作吗？
You think there could possibly be a job like that?

82
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:14,500
能有几种发色？
How many hair colors could there be?

83
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:16,230
五十种？
Fifty?

84
00:06:16,380 --> 00:06:18,140
有人专做这种事
Someone's got that job.

85
00:06:19,300 --> 00:06:20,850
橘子特务
Agent Orange.

86
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,910
我自己取的名字
I came up with that one.

87
00:06:23,470 --> 00:06:25,660
融入了我多变的个性
I apply my personality in a paste.

88
00:06:26,260 --> 00:06:27,850
我倒不以为然
I doubt that very much.

89
00:06:29,070 --> 00:06:30,950
你不了解我
Well, you don't know me, so

90
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:33,380
所以你不会知道的
you don't know, do you?

91
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:39,220
抱歉，我只是…
I'm sorry.

92
00:06:39,370 --> 00:06:40,870
我只是礼貌性回答
I was just trying to be nice.

93
00:06:42,990 --> 00:06:44,310
我懂了
I got it.

94
00:07:03,450 --> 00:07:05,810
对了，我叫克蕾婷（小柑橘）
My name's Clementine, by the way.

95
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:06,930
我叫乔尔
I'm Joel.

96
00:07:07,070 --> 00:07:08,280
嗨，乔尔
Hi, Joel.

97
00:07:08,420 --> 00:07:09,630
你好
no jokes about my name.

98
00:07:09,780 --> 00:07:11,100
别取笑我的名字

99
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:15,510
应该不会啦，你很有礼貌
Oh no. You wouldn't do that.

100
00:07:14,170 --> 00:07:15,690
You're trying to be nice.

101
00:07:16,180 --> 00:07:18,440
我不觉得你的名字好笑
I don't know any jokes about your name.

102
00:07:18,580 --> 00:07:19,970
卡通主题曲
Huckleberry Hound.

103
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,410
我不懂你的意思
I don't know what that means.

104
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,870
卡通啊
Huckleberry Hound?

105
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:26,510
你脑筋秀逗啊？
What are you, nuts?

106
00:07:26,650 --> 00:07:28,280
你有说过
It's been suggested.

107
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:32,390
“亲爱的…亲爱的克蕾婷”
Oh, my darling, oh, my darling, oh, my darling Clementine...

108
00:07:32,530 --> 00:07:35,200
“你消声匿迹了”
You are lost and gone forever, dreadful sorry, Clementine.

109
00:07:35,350 --> 00:07:36,880
“我很遗憾，克蕾婷”

110
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:38,410
没听过吗？

111
00:07:38,550 --> 00:07:40,050
抱歉，只不过…
Sorry. It's a pretty name, though. Really nice.

112
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:42,790
这个名字很好听

113
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:45,640
意思是“仁慈”吧？
It means merciful, right?

114
00:07:46,450 --> 00:07:47,630
仁慈宽厚？
Clemency?

115
00:07:47,770 --> 00:07:49,300
可惜名不副实
Although it hardly fits.

116
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:51,870
我是有仇必报的女人
I'm a vindictive little bitch, truth be told.

117
00:07:52,020 --> 00:07:53,960
天哪，看不出来耶
I wouldn't think that about you.

118
00:07:54,110 --> 00:07:56,500
你怎么可能看出来嘛
Why wouldn't you?

119
00:07:56,650 --> 00:07:58,790
不知道，就是…
I don't know.

120
00:07:59,990 --> 00:08:02,000
不知道，就是…

121
00:08:02,140 --> 00:08:04,120
你看起来人很好
You seemed nice.

122
00:08:04,270 --> 00:08:06,380
我人很好？
now I'm nice?

123
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:09,270
天哪，你没别的形容词了吗？
Don't you know any other adjectives?

124
00:08:09,410 --> 00:08:10,590
我不想当好人
I don't need to be nice.

125
00:08:10,740 --> 00:08:14,110
没这必要，别人也不必对我好
And I don't need anybody to be nice to me.

126
00:08:14,250 --> 00:08:15,740
好吧
Okay.

127
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:20,090
乔尔？
Joel?

128
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:23,190
你叫乔尔，对吧？
It's Joel, right?

129
00:08:23,850 --> 00:08:24,920
对
Yes.

130
00:08:26,780 --> 00:08:28,760
很抱歉刚才对你大小声
I'm sorry I yelled at you.

131
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:31,430
我今天心情不好
I'm a little of out sorts today.

132
00:08:41,350 --> 00:08:43,230
我要承认一件糗事
My embarrassing admission is I really like that you're nice right now.

133
00:08:43,370 --> 00:08:44,870
我喜欢你人很好

134
00:08:45,010 --> 00:08:46,990
现在…

135
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:50,540
不知道下一刻我会怎么想
I can't tell from one moment to the next

136
00:08:49,390 --> 00:08:51,330
what I'm going to like, but...

137
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:53,140
但现在…
right now I'm glad you are.

138
00:08:53,810 --> 00:08:56,580
很庆幸你人很好

139
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:05,110
我有点事…
I have some stuff that I probably should...

140
00:09:05,250 --> 00:09:07,580
可能要…

141
00:09:09,530 --> 00:09:10,470
我正在写…
Oh! I'm sorry.

142
00:09:10,610 --> 00:09:11,550
对不起
Okay. no...

143
00:09:11,690 --> 00:09:12,790
没关系
Sure. That's okay.

144
00:09:12,940 --> 00:09:13,490
没事，我无所谓啦

145
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:15,970
这碰巧是…

146
00:09:16,110 --> 00:09:16,940
好吧

147
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,540
你保重
Take care, then.

148
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:20,340
天哪
Jesus.

149
00:09:33,850 --> 00:09:34,830
嗨!

150
00:09:35,350 --> 00:09:38,130
我可以顺道载你一程
Hi. I could give you a ride if you need.

151
00:09:39,350 --> 00:09:40,320
好冷
It's cold.

152
00:09:40,780 --> 00:09:44,080
对，冷死人了 好吧，快上车
Yeah! Okay.

153
00:09:42,690 --> 00:09:44,190
It is frosty.

154
00:09:44,220 --> 00:09:45,780
你没在跟踪我吧？
You're not a stalker or anything, right?

155
00:09:45,930 --> 00:09:46,830
我没有
I'm not a stalker.

156
00:09:46,970 --> 00:09:48,520
是你先找我搭讪的，记得吗？
You're the one that talked to me, remember?

157
00:09:48,670 --> 00:09:50,750
这是歹徒老掉牙的把戏了
That is the oldest trick in the stalker book

158
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:52,080
是吗？
Really? There's a stalker book?

159
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,920
歹徒还有把戏？

160
00:09:54,070 --> 00:09:55,910
好极了

161
00:09:56,430 --> 00:09:58,240
我倒想研究一下
I've got to read that one.

162
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:06,650
很抱歉我疯疯癫癫的
I'm sorry if I came off sort of nutso.

163
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:08,430
我平常不会这样
I'm not really.

164
00:10:08,580 --> 00:10:09,710
没关系
That's okay. I didn't think you were.

165
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:14,490
我不觉得你疯疯癫癫

166
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,210
要不要喝一杯？
Do you want to have a drink?

167
00:10:19,950 --> 00:10:22,380
我有很多酒可以…
I have lots of drinks, and I could --

168
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:26,040
算了
never mind. That was stupid.

169
00:10:26,180 --> 00:10:27,150
抱歉，是我胡说八道
I'm embarrassed now. Goodnight.

170
00:10:27,290 --> 00:10:27,780
我觉得好丢脸

171
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:28,540
不会啦

172
00:10:28,690 --> 00:10:30,600
晚安

173
00:10:50,260 --> 00:10:52,090
两杯颓废蓝
Two Blue Ruins.

174
00:10:54,260 --> 00:10:55,120
谢谢
Thank you.

175
00:10:55,270 --> 00:10:56,690
干杯吧，年轻人
Drink up, young man.

176
00:10:57,740 --> 00:11:00,620
这样勾引你比较自然
It'll make the whole seduction part less repugnant.

177
00:11:04,490 --> 00:11:05,490
开玩笑啦
I'm just kidding! Come on.

178
00:11:05,630 --> 00:11:07,130
拜托

179
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:16,100
你很沉默寡言
You're kind of closed-mouthed, aren't you?

180
00:11:17,290 --> 00:11:18,750
抱歉，我…
I'm sorry.

181
00:11:18,890 --> 00:11:20,620
我的生活…
You know, my life isn't that interesting.

182
00:11:20,770 --> 00:11:22,190
乏善可陈

183
00:11:22,860 --> 00:11:25,700
每天就是上班和回家
I go to work, I come home...

184
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:28,310
没什么话好说
I don't know what to say.

185
00:11:29,290 --> 00:11:31,130
你应该看看我的日记
You should read my journal.

186
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:33,260
里面几乎是…
It's just... blank

187
00:11:34,510 --> 00:11:35,520
一片空白
Really?

188
00:11:35,660 --> 00:11:36,670
是吗？
Does that make you sad or anxious?

189
00:11:36,810 --> 00:11:39,200
你觉得伤心或焦虑？

190
00:11:39,350 --> 00:11:42,470
我经常焦虑，觉得生活不够充实
I'm always anxious, thinking I'm not living my life to the fullest.

191
00:11:42,620 --> 00:11:44,210
要抱握每个机会
Taking advantage of every possibility and...

192
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:48,280
确定分秒都没浪费
making sure I'm not wasting one second of the little time I have.

193
00:11:48,950 --> 00:11:50,020
我有想过
I think about that.

194
00:11:50,170 --> 00:11:52,220
是吗？

195
00:11:55,350 --> 00:11:57,600
你真的人很好
You're really nice.

196
00:11:58,520 --> 00:12:00,390
天哪，我不能再说这句话了
I have to stop saying that.

197
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:04,050
我要嫁给你
I'm gonna marry you.

198
00:12:04,470 --> 00:12:05,610
我认定了
I know it.

199
00:12:07,910 --> 00:12:09,120
好啊
Okay.

200
00:12:13,830 --> 00:12:18,480
乔尔，改天陪我去查理士河
Joel. You should come up to the Charles with me sometime.

201
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:20,570
这个季节都结冰了
It gets frozen this time of year.

202
00:12:20,710 --> 00:12:21,440
好像很可怕
That sounds scary.

203
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:22,620
对啊
Fxactly.

204
00:12:23,430 --> 00:12:25,160
我会准备点心
I'll pack a picnic - a night picnic

205
00:12:25,690 --> 00:12:26,970
晚上野餐

206
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:29,650
晚上野餐感觉不一样
- night picnics are different.

207
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:31,070
我们可以…
That sounds good.

208
00:12:31,220 --> 00:12:33,020
好主意

209
00:12:33,550 --> 00:12:34,980
但我该走了
But I should go now.

210
00:12:36,930 --> 00:12:38,100
留下来嘛
You should stay.

211
00:12:38,250 --> 00:12:40,750
不行，我真的…
I really have to get up so early and...

212
00:12:40,890 --> 00:12:42,350
我明天要早起

213
00:12:42,490 --> 00:12:44,330
我希望你打电话给我
I would like you to call me.

214
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:45,830
可以吗？
Would you do that?

215
00:12:45,970 --> 00:12:47,220
我很期待
I'd like it.

216
00:12:47,370 --> 00:12:48,720
好
Yes.

217
00:12:52,550 --> 00:12:55,500
打电话来祝我情人节快乐
Wish me a happy Valentine's Day when you call.

218
00:12:55,990 --> 00:12:57,830
我会很感动的
That'd be nice.

219
00:13:38,330 --> 00:13:40,140
你怎么现在才打？
What took you so long?

220
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:41,980
我刚进门
I just walked in.

221
00:13:42,130 --> 00:13:44,240
你想我吗？
You miss me?

222
00:13:46,160 --> 00:13:48,870
很奇怪，我好想你
Oddly enough, I do.

223
00:13:49,020 --> 00:13:50,330
你说你想我
You said I do.

224
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:52,010
我们算是结婚了
I guess that means we're married.

225
00:13:52,150 --> 00:13:53,390
大概吧
I guess so.

226
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:56,800
明晚？去冰上渡蜜月？
Tomorrow night?

227
00:13:56,950 --> 00:13:59,790
这个季节冰层很厚
Honeymoon on Ice?

228
00:13:57,300 --> 00:14:00,180
It's really solid this time of year.

229
00:14:00,250 --> 00:14:01,320
我不知道…
I don't know...

